I can handle it.

266
00:09:36.877 --> 00:09:37.945
What?

267
00:09:38.045 --> 00:09:39.713
Thank you. see you later.

268
00:09:40.681 --> 00:09:43.017
So. how's married life?

269
00:09:43.951 --> 00:09:45.352
He snores so loud.

270
00:09:45.453 --> 00:09:47.655
Yeah. Vikings.

271
00:09:47.755 --> 00:09:49.590
<i>ISAAC:</i>
<i>Okay. Hetty.</i>

272
00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:51.792
that's perfect.

273
00:09:51.892 --> 00:09:53.794
Pete. don't be afraid
to scoot right in there.

274
00:09:53.894 --> 00:09:56.764
All right. now. Sass.
feel free to relax that posture.

275
00:09:56.864 --> 00:09:57.832
