soothing nose whistle.

293
00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:27.962
Hetty. I'm gonna need you
to recreate that.

294
00:10:28.062 --> 00:10:31.198
Oh. unfortunately.
cocaine obliterated my septum.

295
00:10:31.298 --> 00:10:32.534
The air blows through it

296
