303
00:10:48.149 --> 00:10:50.985
I kind of just thought
it would be clumping.

304
00:10:51.085 --> 00:10:52.353
So that's a no to the onion?

305
00:10:52.453 --> 00:10:54.155
Okay. well. somebody

306
00:10:54.255 --> 00:10:55.590
