kind of sad weird.

313
00:11:08.369 --> 00:11:10.037
-Okay. bye.
-ISAAC: Sass.

314
00:11:10.137 --> 00:11:13.741
you can't leave.
Three is not a clump!

315
00:11:13.841 --> 00:11:15.843
All right. Alberta. you're in.

316
00:11:15.943 --> 00:11:17.344
