Dream on. Isaac.

317
00:11:17.444 --> 00:11:19.046
I wish I could.

318
00:11:20.014 --> 00:11:21.650
I wish I could.

319
00:11:23.217 --> 00:11:24.553
<i>JAY:</i>
<i>Well. thank you</i>

320
00:11:24.653 --> 00:11:25.986
