Councilman Heyward.

321
00:11:26.086 --> 00:11:28.088
Always happy
to sit with a constituent.

322
00:11:28.189 --> 00:11:30.057
Unfortunately.
we've seen your happy face.

323
00:11:30.157 --> 00:11:31.560
