and faith of this community.

335
00:11:55.916 --> 00:11:57.718
And unfortunately
my hands are tied.

336
00:11:57.818 --> 00:12:00.120
Not even gonna
touch that one. Too easy.

337
00:12:00.221 --> 00:12:01.455
Okay. I'm gonna
cut right to the chase.

338
00:12:01.556 --> 00:12:03.157
Tad is turning
my dream restaurant

339
00:12:03.257 --> 00:12:04.725
