a DVD to you now...

343
00:12:12.900 --> 00:12:14.636
...that will
make you reconsider.

344
00:12:14.735 --> 00:12:16.804
Aw. baby's first blackmail.

345
00:12:16.904 --> 00:12:18.939
What is this? <i>Swingers?</i>

346
00:12:19.039 --> 00:12:20.307
Well. it's not
the Vince Vaughn love letter

347
00:12:20.407 --> 00:12:21.809
