where that came from.

366
00:12:57.111 --> 00:12:58.012
Well. who is she?

367
00:12:58.112 --> 00:13:00.014
I can't tell you that.

368
00:13:00.114 --> 00:13:01.683
And now that I have this.

369
00:13:01.782 --> 00:13:03.183
I don't have to.

370
00:13:03.284 --> 00:13:05.386
And you won't be able
to prove a thing.

371
