Dude. I have copies.

372
00:13:09.890 --> 00:13:11.191
Oh.

373
00:13:11.292 --> 00:13:12.226
Can I have those?

374
00:13:12.326 --> 00:13:13.628
No.

375
00:13:13.728 --> 00:13:15.697
Okay.

376
00:13:15.796 --> 00:13:17.865
In that case. I'll tell you.

377
00:13:17.965 --> 00:13:19.634
The whistleblower is...

378
