389
00:13:44.858 --> 00:13:46.827
Oh. I-I'm a ghost.
I thought you knew.

390
00:13:46.927 --> 00:13:48.495
Worked at Pizza Barn
back in '05.

391
00:13:48.596 --> 00:13:49.731
Four restaurants ago.

392
00:13:50.097 --> 00:13:51.031
Didn't you see
the check spike in her back?

393
00:13:51.131 --> 00:13:52.433
What's delicious?

394
00:13:52.534 --> 00:13:53.500
I was talking

395
00:13:53.601 --> 00:13:55.603
