439
00:15:32.433 --> 00:15:35.002
So. do we think that
moo shu pork is up for grabs?

440
00:15:35.102 --> 00:15:38.038
-Jay.
-Well. I don't want it
to go to waste.

441
00:15:38.138 --> 00:15:40.140
