442
00:15:47.582 --> 00:15:49.617
-Isaac.
-No. shh. shh. Back to sleep.

443
00:15:49.717 --> 00:15:52.052
-Hey.
-No. no. let's just...
-STUART: Isaac. you're back.

444
00:15:52.152 --> 00:15:54.154
Hey. everyone. Isaac's back.

445
00:15:54.254 --> 00:15:58.860
Oh. Look who came crawling back.
standing up.

446
00:15:58.959 --> 00:16:02.129
No. no. no. no. I'm not back.
I simply want to sleep with you.

447
00:16:02.229 --> 00:16:04.031
-Listening.
-Uh. no. I mean.

448
00:16:04.131 --> 00:16:05.966
I've been having trouble
sleeping upstairs.

449
00:16:06.066 --> 00:16:09.470
so I thought I would just come
down here to get some shut-eye.

450
00:16:09.571 --> 00:16:12.206
Yeah. right.
I know what this is.

451
00:16:12.306 --> 00:16:13.974
-You miss us.
-(Isaac scoffs)

452
00:16:14.074 --> 00:16:15.710
Yeah. right.
What do I miss. hmm?

453
00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:17.211
