456
00:16:21.850 --> 00:16:24.886
Okay. fine. I miss you freaks.
There. I said it.

457
00:16:24.985 --> 00:16:27.522
Isaac. just because you
don't live down here anymore

458
00:16:27.622 --> 00:16:29.056
doesn't mean
you can't come visit.

459
00:16:29.156 --> 00:16:31.325
-Really?
-Absolutely.

460
00:16:31.425 --> 00:16:33.695
We have an open-door policy
down in the pit.

461
00:16:33.795 --> 00:16:35.663
Mostly because someone
nailed a door shut

462
00:16:35.763 --> 00:16:37.030
