468
00:16:50.344 --> 00:16:52.412
(Isaac sighs)

469
00:16:52.514 --> 00:16:53.581
(ghosts snore)

470
00:16:53.681 --> 00:16:56.918
So I could be mayor again

471
00:16:57.017 --> 00:16:59.921
